## Patterns & methodology

### Agent design patterns
- Reference: AgentPatterns.ai — https://www.agentpatterns.ai
- Influence: general vocabulary and framing for recurring multi-agent and
  agent-workflow patterns (planner/executor separation, verification loops,
  role specialization). splock's subagent roster (planner, coder, reviewer,
  verifier, recon, research, qa, qna) and its completion-gate loop are an
  independent realization of ideas in this space rather than a port of any
  specific pattern catalog.

