## A note on provenance

splock was extracted into a standalone, repo-agnostic plugin from a private
in-house automation framework. During extraction every host-specific identity,
path, organization name, and domain token was scrubbed from the tree, and a
dedicated trace-grep gate (`tests/trace_grep.sh`) enforces that the published
artifact carries none of that provenance. If you find a stray host reference,
please open an issue — it is a bug in the scrub, not an intended attribution.
